Crowd,is,a,Remote,API,for,Atlassian,s,Single,Sign,On,Software,The,API,makes,basic,HTTP,requests,with,the,default,response,in,XML,However,the,API,can,be,configured,to,return,JSON,instead,This,REST,API,is,based,on,open,standards,so,it,can,accept,any,programming,language,A,few,of,the,features,the,Crowd,Remote,API,offers,are,user,authentication,retrieving,adding,updating,and,removing,users,updating,a,user,s,password,and,requesting,a,password,reset,retrieving,adding,updating,and,removing,groups